Package: dnspilot
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: DNS Pilot Maintainers <maintainers@dnspilot.io>
Depends: libc6, libgcc-s1, libx11-6, libxcb1, libxkbcommon0, libwayland-client0
Description: DNS benchmark and resolver guidance
 DNS Pilot benchmarks DNS resolvers, manages custom DNS profiles, renders
 diagnostics, and provides store-safe manual DNS settings guidance. Native DNS
 mutation is unavailable in this build.
